{"tid":1084981,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"人年紀愈大係唔係愈鍾意買特價貨？","createTime":"2019-03-30T19:53:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-05T19:19:06.000Z","uid":91835,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ca74ae59c7ed37bda4ab5cdb5f4ba9aa3c015fa1","tid":1084981,"uid":91835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T19:53:17.000Z","msg":"話說我老豆係百佳買咗一堆特價野返屋企，有朱古力、公仔麵等等，但係我同細佬都唔係幾想食，佢以前好似唔會特登買特價野<br />\n<br />\n係唔係上咗年紀既人就會開始鍾意買平野？師奶，爺爺嫲嫲⋯⋯你講過一次鍾意食咩餸，就會成日整果樣餸，或者買定好多生果擺係屋企，但係食唔哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9aa8ea0c42ea1836d42a816228e584675834c7a","tid":1084981,"uid":6097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T19:59:28.000Z","msg":"怕你餓親啫"},{"pid":"e63583de8ec5ba7261992816690284f0637f4405","tid":1084981,"uid":245126,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T20:02:03.000Z","msg":"我細個開始已經鐘意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 師奶仔性格"},{"pid":"8fbea12f08aaceaf6e6c1b440bf5c65fabaf699a","tid":1084981,"uid":91835,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e63583de8ec5ba7261992816690284f0637f4405","tid":1084981,"uid":245126,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T20:02:03.000Z","msg":"我細個開始已經鐘意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 師奶仔性格"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T20:36:01.000Z","msg":"問題係我老竇因為盒朱古力特價，所以一次買咗五盒；但嗰隻朱古力其實我同我細佬都麻麻哋，我細佬淨係食黑朱古力"},{"pid":"f3e4908d3812f351919a21de9db11f33d1707f4d","tid":1084981,"uid":91835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9aa8ea0c42ea1836d42a816228e584675834c7a","tid":1084981,"uid":6097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T19:59:28.000Z","msg":"怕你餓親啫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T20:36:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a89eef8df3e005c577f4c7bbdf61803afe68ec7","tid":1084981,"uid":235520,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T20:48:57.000Z","msg":"我係 特價真係平好多 <br />\n有好多新野未試過都會特登買黎試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c5ceac587dbc92ccfb8859d3bacd4d97e90e03a","tid":1084981,"uid":105066,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T21:44:02.000Z","msg":"特價野邊個唔鐘意？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />降低左入手門檻 有閒錢咪試下"},{"pid":"f81d9df07c6a32586d50ec0c5764440945a215b7","tid":1084981,"uid":191815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T22:44:36.000Z","msg":"唔買通常怕就到期擺唔得耐<br />\n除非有信心買咗返嚟即刻食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e3d8537dec8671ae2ae9cfe2bd2aa78bd587305","tid":1084981,"uid":151071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T02:01:11.000Z","msg":"窮"},{"pid":"29bf074e9632bc4078bc410d0a4f6a0b14de914d","tid":1084981,"uid":91835,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f81d9df07c6a32586d50ec0c5764440945a215b7","tid":1084981,"uid":191815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T22:44:36.000Z","msg":"唔買通常怕就到期擺唔得耐<br />\n除非有信心買咗返嚟即刻食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T19:19:06.000Z","msg":"我都係<br />\n睇過本講心理學嘅書，雖然價錢平左，但都會令人買多咗唔需要嘅嘢，然後擺擺下就過期<br />\n食物好少買特價，不過特價衫我一定買<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}